quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  41,19,Ve yevme yuhĆeru aÂŽdaĂŒllahi ilen nari fe hĂŒm yuzeun
  41,20,Hatta iza ma cauha Ćehide aleyhim semÂŽuhĂŒm ve ebsaruhĂŒm ve cĂŒludĂŒhĂŒm bima kanu yaÂŽmelun
  41,21,Ve kalu li cĂŒhudihim lime ĆehidtĂŒm aleyna kalu entaknellahĂŒllezÄ± entaka kĂŒlle ĆeyÂŽiv ve hĂŒve halekakĂŒm evvele merrativ ve ileyhi tĂŒrceun
  41,22,Ve ma kĂŒntĂŒm testetirune ey yeĆhede aleykĂŒm semÂŽukĂŒm ve la ebsarukĂŒm ve la cĂŒludĂŒkĂŒm ve lakin zanentĂŒm ennellahe la yaÂŽlemĂŒ kesÄ±ram mimma taÂŽmelun
  41,23,Ve zalikĂŒm zannĂŒkĂŒmĂŒllezÄ± zanentĂŒm bi rabbikĂŒm erdakĂŒm fe asbahtĂŒm minel hasirÄ±n
  41,24,Fe iy yasbiru fen naru mesvel lehĂŒm ve iy yestaÂŽtibu femahĂŒm minel muÂŽtebÄ±n
  41,25,Ve kayyadna lehĂŒm kuranae fezeyyenu lehĂŒm ma beyne eydÄ±him ve ma halfehĂŒm ve hakka aleyhimĂŒl kavlĂŒ fÄ± ĂŒmemin kad halet min kablihim minel cinni vel ins innehĂŒm kanu hasirÄ±n